IOS 13.3 beta 1 for developers has been released. What's new
05 Nov 2019, 21:08 by Artyom Bausov
Apple has released iOS 13.3 beta 1 for authorized developers.
Build number is 17C5032d.
Judging by the description, this update fixed bugs and increased the overall stability of the operating system. At the time of writing, there was no more information.



What's new:
‚Ä¢ fixed the work of RAM ‚Ä¢ a toggle switch appeared to disable the animoji keyboard
The update size is about 4 GB. You can download iOS 13.3 beta 1 now "over the air." Only a developer profile is needed.

Easy update!
